It can be done.

00:25:04.410 --> 00:25:08.840
They're out there,
the sites that work fine.

00:25:08.840 --> 00:25:16.840
But most sites, at least that I
looked at, did not work as desired.

00:25:19.090 --> 00:25:27.090
So what solutions can you
implement on your WordPress menu?

00:25:29.380 --> 00:25:30.250
Let's take a look at it.

00:25:30.250 --> 00:25:34.040
Well, you can do
some PHP remediation.

00:25:35.100 --> 00:25:39.750
And what you'll want to
